Package: regsplice
Title: Lasso-based Methods to Detect Differential Exon Usage
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: person("Lukas M.", "Weber", email = "lukmweber@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Statistical methods for detection of differential exon usage
    (differential splicing) in RNA sequencing (RNA-seq) or microarray data sets,
    using L1 regularization (lasso) to improve power.
